elements.name: TC1_Add item list in Shopping List Application
elements.description: To validate whether user is able add product in shoppinglist application.

steps.name: the user has Launched "Shopping List" application in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user clicks on "Layout with Add item" button in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user verifies whether "My Shopping List" tab is "present" in "shoppingApplication" page. (Continue on Failure)
the user clicks on "Open Navigation Drawer" button in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user clicks on "New List" button in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user verifies whether "New Shopping List Title" tab is "present" in "shoppingApplication" page. (Continue on Failure)
the user enters "ShoppingList name" in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user clicks on "OK" button in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user enters "item name" in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user clicks on "ADD" button in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user hides the keyboard if present and then clicks on "Open Navigation Drawer" button in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user clicks on "New List" button in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user enters "ShoppingList name1" in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user clicks on "OK" button in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user enters "item name1" in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user clicks on "ADD" button in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user clicks on "More Option" button in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user clicks on "Delete List" button in "shoppingApplication" page.
the user verifies whether "Delete popUp Title" tab is "present" in "shoppingApplication" page. (Continue on Failure)
the user clicks on "OK" button in "shoppingApplication" page.
